In the sign of the "European Year of Equal Opportunity" to be guaranteed for all, the purpose of the European Summit for Equal Opportunities organized each year, from the Berlin meeting last year, is to ensure a single forum to promote the goals of anti-discrimination and equal opportunities set at the state and European level.
